Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本作品是假定首都圈内发生强烈地震，\N以大量的研究和验证为基础制作的虚构故事。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了追求真实性，我们在构造原创故事时已做\N过很多模拟，但在演出上仍会有与真实情况不符之处。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.13,0:01:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,01 报告状况
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正要开始消防作业
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在芝公园内正在派发东京都和港区的救援物资
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.65,0:01:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家根据指示 前往芝公园
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.32,0:02:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受伤的人请在这里等待
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一遍  现在芝公园内正在…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有 是下一班船
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有五分钟就能到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.37,0:02:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走到芝公园大约要十五分钟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.45,0:02:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来 脚磨破的地方还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.16,0:02:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天下午15点46分左右
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以关东地区为中心发生了强烈地震
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.23,0:02:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次地震的震源是在东京湾北部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震源深度约25千米
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.54,0:02:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示地震规模的震级据推测达到里氏8.0
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 能看到东京塔了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:02:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就能到家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.35,0:03:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还早啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是从我们家也能看到东京塔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那离我们家也还很远
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来 没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 公园里有能洗手什么的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想厕所是应该有的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不知道有没有水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里弄脏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到家之后 把我的布丁给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然说这个干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以加油走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 我还没幼稚到会被点心引诱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗谁啊 你明明就是点心军曹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点心军曹？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一下有点糟…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:04:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来 你是肚子疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛可不要忍着 要说出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你稍等一下 我去那边看看很快就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等回了家 我们去北海道的爷爷家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后吃牛奶雪糕什么的 还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年去不成北海道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.77,0:04:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来 抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是吃蛋糕把肚子吃坏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 便携厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 这是厕所吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是用纸做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用的时候就说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何地方都能用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我现在还好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.23,0:05:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要便携厕所和湿纸巾请来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要便携厕所和湿纸巾请来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厕所 厕所在…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那边好像能拿到吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边正在派发救援物资
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请每人来领取一份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是那边在派发
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 有杯面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才这次震得挺厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先找个地方休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边呢 是帐篷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.57,0:06:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是厕所啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在那边的树荫下等你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 她到底忍了多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:06:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这边有空位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机超好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来的别插队啊 好好排队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 这里空着的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看后面就知道了吧 别想糊弄过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被人插了队也说点什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别拿小鬼说事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小孩子面前你就不觉得羞耻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底几岁了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想问你几岁了 混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.71,0:07:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为你插队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还打不通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能早点联系上小雏就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说点心军曹没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:08:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理…小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边有巧克力和便携食品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去拿拉面吧 拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 这边帐篷的杯面派发完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人拿了两个走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 也是有那种大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对小孩子指手划脚 自己却那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.69,0:08:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是有什么原因吧 比如有受伤的人在等他之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.33,0:08:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫 烫死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来 没事吧 有没有烫伤？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分 连声对不起都不说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（防灾用真空包）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请拿好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 跟我的换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟你说不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说没人认领的都运到这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:10:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是这个地区去世的人运到这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在知道三茶怎么样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三茶啊 有三茶的情况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 三茶的消息还没到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（正在拨号 妈妈的手机）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（请稍等）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要到什么时候才能接通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,种在学校的七叶树不知怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸妈妈没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点事你自己也知道吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来 悠贵君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之回家的路应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们现在在的芝公园
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是涩谷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往这一直走 就是我家在的三轩茶屋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那穿过世田谷区大道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这拐弯就是砧公园了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那再走一会就到你们家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们先一起去三轩茶屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再走一段路就到我们家了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神上路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来也加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定到学校手机就能通了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不懂你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵君肯定是想要是能通就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想着那样姐姐也会开心点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去丢下垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来我们就走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真心灵相通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和真理小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好点了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等回到家 不止布丁…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 能不能别老讲吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然肚子还疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么了 再过一会能就回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟你说这不是「一会」就能到的嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.83,0:13:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 就算回到了家也不知道家里是不是平安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸妈妈也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这么给他们打电话也不打个过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为电话还…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能根本就不担心我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.79,0:13:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:13:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是够了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:13:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你这种地方最让人来气！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么想说的就说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛总要看人家的脸色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底都怪你要来看机器人展才会这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是想看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是想看桥嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是暑假 却什么地方也不带我们去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才想和姐姐…一起来看桥的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…到底跑到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 终于给我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你们两个都不见了 让我好找
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.29,0:15:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我去找下他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等… 未来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚的余震不小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有房子倒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这个了 妈妈很害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:15:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.11,0:16:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵 我叫你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理小姐已经回来了 我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐根本就不懂我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要到东京铁塔上看家怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家的路也知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道回家的路也不知家里是不是还平安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.47,0:16:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想看看家怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐要是知道家里没事也能放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.44,0:17:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对能看到我们家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我们家都能看到东京塔的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 这也一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 爸爸妈妈没有死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见爸爸妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹你们就两个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是这个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是联系不上而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.45,0:18:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点回家把礼物送给妈妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.49,0:19:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.63,0:19:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.91,0:19:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠…贵？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别耍姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.21,0:19:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.36,0:20:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把受伤的人带到芝公园去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.59,0:20:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能动的人请来帮忙！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁到这来帮帮忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵君肿了个包 没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.14,0:20:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.48,0:20:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这么坦率很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在台场的约定 现在开始好好遵守哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.39,0:20:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那我们现在去避难所的中学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自拿好自己的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.29,0:20:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得赶在太阳落山前到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.43,0:20:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了我们的约定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:21:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.76,0:22:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待救援的受灾者现在集中在港区的学校避难所
